http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Country-made-pistol-mobile-phones-seized/article13987436.ece

The police seized a country-made pistol along with nine rounds of fire and three mobile handsets from a 22-year-old youth in Kudachi of Raibag taluk on Thursday.The police said that they were tipped off about the accused, who was identified as Rohit Padoriya, a resident of Ichalkaranji, a taluk in neighbouring Kolhapur district in Maharashtra. The police also seized a car in which he had come to Kudachi.The accused was produced before court which remanded him in police custody for further investigation, the police said and declined to share more information stating that the matter was under investigation.